    "body": "I think the correct syntax is either `sumContract.sum(1,2, {from:web3.eth.accounts[0],gas:utils.DEFAULT_TX_COST})` or `sumContract.sum(1,2).sendTransaction({from:web3.eth.accounts[0],gas:utils.DEFAULT_TX_COST})`\n\nIf you use `call` you certainly do not get persisting changes to storage.\n",
